data.message: BrandForge: Implement template compatibility gating with auto column mapping: Created template-compatibility.ts library with column name normalization, alias matching, and compatibility checking. Updated batch creation API to filter templates based on CSV column compatibility and auto-map columns to slots. UI now shows compatible/incompatible templates with slot mappings. Pass rate should improve significantly.
